               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols.
                     5ra-219rb) 
 I-1) Maggābit (fols. 5ra-37rc)
 I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     37va-65rc)
 I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 65ra-103rc)
 I-4) Sane (fols.
                     103ra-138va)
 I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 139ra-182rc)
 I-6) Naḥāse (fols.
                     182ra-212vc)
 I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 213ra-219rb)
 
 Additiones
                     1-3.</summary>
